title: Tech News: Google I/O Highlights
itunes:title: Tech News: Google I/O Highlights
description:
Google held a virtual event for developers and we learned about a lot of software updates, but not much on hardware. Cryptocurrency values went through a major dip. And ByteDance has a new leader. All this and more.
